{
  "info": {
    "name": "Gudang Planet — Operational API (v2)",
    "description": "Collection untuk modul Operasional Gudang Planet.\n\n**Base URL:** `{{base_url}}/api/v1/operational`\n\n**Auth:** Bearer token dari `POST /api/v1/login` (phone + password).\n\n**Alur bisnis terbaru:**\n- **Admin Income** — pemasukan pusat, `mandor_uuid` & `sub_company_uuid` opsional (atribusi saja), `source_type: INTERNAL`\n- **Admin Expense INTERNAL** — pengeluaran pusat\n- **Admin Expense MANDOR** — transfer ke mandor → buat income pending + notifikasi\n- **Mandor Income** — pemasukan cabang sendiri, langsung kredit wallet\n- **Mandor Expense** — pengeluaran internal cabang, debit wallet\n\n**Upload bukti:** jpg/jpeg/png/pdf, maks **10MB**\n\n**GET show:** jika UUID tidak ditemukan → `data: []` (bukan 404)\n\n**Demo credentials (company 1):**\n| Role | Phone | Password |\n|------|-------|----------|\n| ADMIN | 081122223333 | admin_gp |\n| MANDOR | 082233334444 | mandor_gp |",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url", "value": "http://localhost:8000", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "token", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "uuid", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "sub_company_uuid", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "mandor_uuid", "value": "", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{token}}", "type": "string" }]
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login (Admin)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.data && json.data.token) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.data.token);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"081122223333\",\n  \"password\": \"admin_gp\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/login",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Login sebagai ADMIN. Token otomatis disimpan ke collection variable `token`."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (Mandor)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.data && json.data.token) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.data.token);",
                  "}",
                  "if (json.data && json.data.user && json.data.user.sub_companies && json.data.user.sub_companies.length) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('sub_company_uuid', json.data.user.sub_companies[0].uuid);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"082233334444\",\n  \"password\": \"mandor_gp\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/login",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Login sebagai MANDOR. Token & `sub_company_uuid` pertama otomatis disimpan."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/logout",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "logout"]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Dashboard",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Admin Dashboard",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/operational/dashboard/admin?date_from=&date_to=",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "operational", "dashboard", "admin"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "date_from", "value": "", "description": "YYYY-MM-DD, default: today" },
                { "key": "date_to", "value": "", "description": "YYYY-MM-DD, harus bulan yang sama dengan date_from" },
                { "key": "sub_company_uuid", "value": "", "disabled": true, "description": "Filter agregat ke cabang tertentu" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Ringkasan dashboard admin + list `sub_companies` (total income/expense per cabang untuk drill-down read-only).\n\nRole: SUPERADMIN, OWNER, ADMIN."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Mandor Dashboard",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/operational/dashboard/mandor",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "operational", "dashboard", "mandor"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "date_from", "value": "", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "date_to", "value": "", "disabled": true }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Ringkasan dashboard mandor. Role: MANDOR, KEPALA_MANDOR."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Sub Companies",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "List Sub Companies",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/sub-companies",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "sub-companies"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "mandor_uuid", "value": "", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "is_active", "value": "true", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "search", "value": "", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "per_page", "value": "15", "disabled": true }
              ]
            },
            "description": "List cabang operasional. Mandor/KEPALA_MANDOR hanya melihat cabang sendiri (KEPALA_MANDOR melihat semua cabang via unscoped query)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Show Sub Company",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/sub-companies/{{sub_company_uuid}}",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "sub-companies", "{{sub_company_uuid}}"]
            },
            "description": "Detail cabang. Jika UUID tidak ditemukan → `data: []`."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Create Sub Company + Mandor",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"mandor\": {\n    \"name\": \"Mandor Baru\",\n    \"phone\": \"081234567890\",\n    \"email\": \"mandor@test.com\",\n    \"address\": \"Jl. Mandor No. 1\",\n    \"role\": \"MANDOR\"\n  },\n  \"sub_company\": {\n    \"name\": \"Cabang Jakarta\",\n    \"address\": \"Jl. Cabang Jakarta No. 2\"\n  }\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/sub-companies",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "operational", "sub-companies"]
            },
            "description": "Buat cabang operasional sekaligus mandor baru. Kode cabang auto-generate. Return credentials mandor.\n\n`mandor.role` (opsional): `MANDOR` (default) atau `KEPALA_MANDOR`.\n\nRole: SUPERADMIN, OWNER, ADMIN."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Incomes",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "List Incomes",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/operational/incomes",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "operational", "incomes"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "sub_company_uuid", "value": "{{sub_company_uuid}}", "disabled": true, "description": "Drill-down per cabang (read-only)" },
                { "key": "date_from", "value": "", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "date_to", "value": "", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "mandor_uuid", "value": "", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "source_type", "value": "INTERNAL", "disabled": true, "description": "INTERNAL | MANDOR" },
                { "key": "search", "value": "", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "order_by_key", "value": "date", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "order_by_value", "value": "DESC", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "per_page", "value": "15", "disabled": true }
              ]
            },
            "description": "List pemasukan. Mandor/KEPALA_MANDOR otomatis di-scope ke cabang sendiri."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Create Income (Admin — Pusat)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                { "key": "name", "value": "Pemasukan Pusat", "type": "text", "description": "Required" },
                { "key": "amount", "value": "500000", "type": "text", "description": "Required, numeric" },
                { "key": "date", "value": "2026-06-16", "type": "text", "description": "Required, YYYY-MM-DD" },
                { "key": "proof_file", "value": "", "type": "file", "description": "Required, jpg/jpeg/png/pdf max 10MB" },
                { "key": "note", "value": "", "type": "text", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "mandor_uuid", "value": "", "type": "text", "disabled": true, "description": "Optional — atribusi ke mandor/cabang" },
                { "key": "sub_company_uuid", "value": "", "type": "text", "disabled": true, "description": "Required if mandor_uuid diisi" }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/operational/incomes",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "operational", "incomes"]
            },
            "description": "Admin catat pemasukan pusat (`source_type: INTERNAL`). **Tidak** membuat transfer/konfirmasi mandor.\n\n`mandor_uuid` & `sub_company_uuid` opsional (hanya atribusi).\n\nRole: SUPERADMIN, OWNER, ADMIN."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Create Income (Admin — Dengan Atribusi Mandor)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                { "key": "mandor_uuid", "value": "{{mandor_uuid}}", "type": "text", "description": "Optional" },
                { "key": "sub_company_uuid", "value": "{{sub_company_uuid}}", "type": "text", "description": "Required if mandor_uuid" },
                { "key": "name", "value": "Pemasukan Atribusi Cabang", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "amount", "value": "200000", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "date", "value": "2026-06-16", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "proof_file", "value": "", "type": "file", "description": "max 10MB" },
                { "key": "note", "value": "", "type": "text", "disabled": true }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/operational/incomes",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "operational", "incomes"]
            },
            "description": "Admin income dengan atribusi mandor/cabang. Tetap `INTERNAL`, tanpa transfer confirmation."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Create Income (Mandor)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                { "key": "sub_company_uuid", "value": "{{sub_company_uuid}}", "type": "text", "description": "Required" },
                { "key": "name", "value": "Pemasukan Cabang", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "amount", "value": "150000", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "date", "value": "2026-06-16", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "proof_file", "value": "", "type": "file", "description": "max 10MB" },
                { "key": "note", "value": "", "type": "text", "disabled": true }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/operational/incomes",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "operational", "incomes"]
            },
            "description": "Mandor catat pemasukan cabang sendiri. `INTERNAL` + langsung kredit wallet.\n\nRole: MANDOR, KEPALA_MANDOR."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Show Income",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/operational/incomes/{{uuid}}",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "operational", "incomes", "{{uuid}}"]
            },
            "description": "Detail income. Jika UUID tidak ditemukan → `data: []`."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update Income (Admin)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                { "key": "name", "value": "", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "amount", "value": "", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "date", "value": "", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "proof_file", "value": "", "type": "file", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "note", "value": "", "type": "text", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "reason", "value": "Koreksi data", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "mandor_uuid", "value": "", "type": "text", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "sub_company_uuid", "value": "", "type": "text", "disabled": true }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/operational/incomes/{{uuid}}",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "operational", "incomes", "{{uuid}}"]
            },
            "description": "Update income pusat admin (`INTERNAL` only). Income transfer mandor (`MANDOR`) tidak bisa diedit dari sini."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update Income (Mandor)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                { "key": "sub_company_uuid", "value": "", "type": "text", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "name", "value": "", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "amount", "value": "", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "date", "value": "", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "proof_file", "value": "", "type": "file", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "note", "value": "", "type": "text", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "reason", "value": "", "type": "text", "disabled": true }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/operational/incomes/{{uuid}}",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "operational", "incomes", "{{uuid}}"]
            },
            "description": "Update income mandor. Hanya `INTERNAL` (bukan transfer dari admin). Adjust wallet."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Delete Income (Admin)",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/operational/incomes/{{uuid}}",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "operational", "incomes", "{{uuid}}"]
            },
            "description": "Hapus income pusat admin (`INTERNAL` only)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Delete Income (Mandor)",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/operational/incomes/{{uuid}}",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "operational", "incomes", "{{uuid}}"]
            },
            "description": "Hapus income mandor (`INTERNAL` only). Refund wallet."
          }
        }
      ],
      "description": "Pemasukan — satu endpoint, logic berbeda per role.\n\n- Admin: pemasukan pusat (INTERNAL), mandor opsional\n- Mandor: pemasukan cabang sendiri (INTERNAL) + terima transfer admin (MANDOR, read-only/edit via konfirmasi)"
    },
    {
      "name": "Expenses",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "List Expenses",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/operational/expenses",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "operational", "expenses"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "sub_company_uuid", "value": "{{sub_company_uuid}}", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "expense_type", "value": "INTERNAL", "disabled": true, "description": "INTERNAL | MANDOR" },
                { "key": "date_from", "value": "", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "date_to", "value": "", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "mandor_uuid", "value": "", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "search", "value": "", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "order_by_key", "value": "date", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "order_by_value", "value": "DESC", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "per_page", "value": "15", "disabled": true }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Create Expense (Admin — INTERNAL Pusat)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                { "key": "expense_type", "value": "INTERNAL", "type": "text", "description": "Required" },
                { "key": "name", "value": "Pengeluaran Pusat", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "amount", "value": "100000", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "date", "value": "2026-06-16", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "proof_file", "value": "", "type": "file", "description": "max 10MB" },
                { "key": "note", "value": "", "type": "text", "disabled": true }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/operational/expenses",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "operational", "expenses"]
            },
            "description": "Pengeluaran internal pusat. Tanpa mandor/sub_company."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Create Expense (Admin — Transfer ke Mandor)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                { "key": "expense_type", "value": "MANDOR", "type": "text", "description": "Required" },
                { "key": "mandor_uuid", "value": "{{mandor_uuid}}", "type": "text", "description": "Required" },
                { "key": "sub_company_uuid", "value": "{{sub_company_uuid}}", "type": "text", "description": "Required" },
                { "key": "name", "value": "Transfer Dana ke Mandor", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "amount", "value": "250000", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "date", "value": "2026-06-16", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "proof_file", "value": "", "type": "file", "description": "max 10MB" },
                { "key": "note", "value": "", "type": "text", "disabled": true }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/operational/expenses",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "operational", "expenses"]
            },
            "description": "Transfer ke mandor. Membuat expense `MANDOR` + income pending + notifikasi ke mandor.\n\nResponse includes `transfer_income` dengan `transfer_confirmation.status: PENDING`."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Create Expense (Mandor — Internal Cabang)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                { "key": "sub_company_uuid", "value": "{{sub_company_uuid}}", "type": "text", "description": "Required" },
                { "key": "name", "value": "Pengeluaran Cabang", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "amount", "value": "50000", "type": "text", "description": "Cek saldo wallet cukup" },
                { "key": "date", "value": "2026-06-16", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "proof_file", "value": "", "type": "file", "description": "max 10MB" },
                { "key": "note", "value": "", "type": "text", "disabled": true }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/operational/expenses",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "operational", "expenses"]
            },
            "description": "Pengeluaran internal cabang mandor. Debit wallet, notify admin jika saldo tidak cukup."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Show Expense",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/operational/expenses/{{uuid}}",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "operational", "expenses", "{{uuid}}"]
            },
            "description": "Detail expense. Jika UUID tidak ditemukan → `data: []`."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update Expense (Admin — INTERNAL)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                { "key": "name", "value": "", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "amount", "value": "", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "date", "value": "", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "proof_file", "value": "", "type": "file", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "note", "value": "", "type": "text", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "reason", "value": "Koreksi data", "type": "text" }
              ]
